        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/g/8baadc/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2017-07-10T21:01:26.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>This is (ok, tasted only once) a good wine - however \u2026 be aware that this is kind of a charity auction \u2026 you won\u00b4t get the equivalent in taste for what you pay \u2026 tastes like 20-25 Euro good Bourgogne<br>\n(I prefer the Bouzeron of Aubert de Villlaine \u2026)</p>",
