        "created_at": "2017-07-12T18:51:14.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I tasted the 2012 in spring in a restaurant.  While it is a very good Haut-C\u00f4tes de Nuits it has nothing to do with the Montrachet of DRC.  I agree with Gerhard that the Bouzeron of Domaine de Villaine is better Q/P.</p>",
